Day 1: Starting with Python (Core Fundamentals)

Day 1 was dedicated to mastering the absolute basics of the Python language. 
This module established the foundation required for all future development, covering basic input/output,
variable management, mathematical operations, and essential control flow using if/else statements.

   Directory Contents (Day 1)

